00:14:11,481 --> 00:14:12,521
nothing can go wrong.

291
00:14:14,442 --> 00:14:15,762
That's right, Your Majesty.

292
00:14:16,122 --> 00:14:17,762
It's not your problem if the princess

293
00:14:18,281 --> 00:14:19,882
goes to Chenrong Mountain.

294
00:14:20,281 --> 00:14:21,521
It's someone else's problem.

295
00:14:27,362 --> 00:14:29,721
How many days has it been
since we sent the letter?

296
00:14:31,242 --> 00:14:32,041
It's been

297
00:14:32,521 --> 00:14:33,442
seven days.

298
00:14:35,122 --> 00:14:37,202
And His Majesty hasn't replied?

299
00:14:37,762 --> 00:14:38,401
No.

300
00:14:40,322 --> 00:14:41,202
Miss Shen

301
00:14:41,202 --> 00:14:42,641
is truly blessed.

302
00:14:43,041 --> 00:14:44,922
Everyone thought that
her marriage to His Majesty

303
00:14:44,922 --> 00:14:45,721
was a mistake.

304
00:14:46,081 --> 00:14:47,601
But His Majesty ascended the throne

305
00:14:47,601 --> 00:14:48,721
and became the King of Xiyan.

306
00:14:49,081 --> 00:14:50,202
Just for the sake of

307
00:14:50,202 --> 00:14:51,922
all the hardships they've been through,

308
00:14:52,161 --> 00:14:52,961
Miss Shen could

309
00:14:53,002 --> 00:14:54,242
become the Queen of Xiyan.

310
00:14:54,961 --> 00:14:56,481
Stop calling her "Miss Shen".

311
00:14:56,762 --> 00:14:57,442
Now,

312
00:14:57,442 --> 00:14:58,841
she is the consort of the King.

313
00:14:59,242 --> 00:15:00,601
Even Miss Xinyue has to pay respects

314
00:15:00,601 --> 00:15:01,882
and greet her accordingly.

315
00:15:04,202 --> 00:15:05,721
Who allowed you to gossip here?

316
00:15:06,961 --> 00:15:07,641
Miss.

317
00:15:08,521 --> 00:15:09,281
Go away.

318
00:15:09,802 --> 00:15:10,562
- Yes.
- Yes.

319
00:15:15,961 --> 00:15:16,721
Miss.

320
00:15:17,202 --> 00:15:18,161
His Majesty needs

321
00:15:18,202 --> 00:15:19,202
a queen by his side.

322
00:15:19,521 --> 00:15:20,562
All the major clans of Xiyan,

323
00:15:21,041 --> 00:15:22,762
let alone the ones
in the Central Plains,

324
00:15:22,762 --> 00:15:24,122
intend to send someone to His Majesty.

325
00:15:24,721 --> 00:15:26,442
You should make plans early.

326
00:15:26,521 --> 00:15:27,802
Which lady from any major clan

327
00:15:28,442 --> 00:15:29,562
can be more distinguished

328
00:15:29,641 --> 00:15:30,521
than me?

329
00:15:31,041 --> 00:15:32,762
Those women are not worth concern.

330
00:15:33,362 --> 00:15:34,682
But what about the Princess

331
00:15:35,202 --> 00:15:36,961
from Wushen Mountain
who clings to His Majesty?

332
00:15:41,802 --> 00:15:43,122
Haoling Yi.

333
00:15:46,961 --> 00:15:48,521
(Following His Majesty's sacred decree,)

334
00:15:48,841 --> 00:15:50,242
(the populations and land ownership)

335
00:15:50,562 --> 00:15:51,721
(throughout the Central Plains)

336
00:15:51,882 --> 00:15:52,961
have been fully tallied

337
00:15:53,202 --> 00:15:54,202
and documented.

338
00:15:54,721 --> 00:15:56,762
Please take a look.

339
00:16:08,048 --> 00:16:10,064
(Xiyan Deyan, Xiyan Yuyang)

340
00:16:12,281 --> 00:16:12,802
Your Majesty,

341
00:16:13,521 --> 00:16:14,721
(Chief of Huhe)
I have something to report.

342
00:16:15,002 --> 00:16:15,600
Speak.

343
00:16:16,122 --> 00:16:17,762
You've stayed in the Central Plains

344
00:16:17,841 --> 00:16:18,882
since your ascension.

345
00:16:19,202 --> 00:16:20,281
(Chishui Fenglong, Chenrong Yi)
This place may be prosperous,

346
00:16:20,401 --> 00:16:21,841
but Xiyan Town is the capital.

347
00:16:22,002 --> 00:16:23,481
Your Majesty,

348
00:16:24,242 --> 00:16:25,281
please return to Xiyan Town.

349
00:16:25,601 --> 00:16:26,762
Seconded.

350
00:16:26,882 --> 00:16:28,322
Seconded.

351
00:16:28,401 --> 00:16:31,362
- Please return to Xiyan Town.
- Please return to Xiyan Town.

352
00:16:32,330 --> 00:16:34,202
(Chief of Shangyang)

353
00:16:34,202 --> 00:16:34,762
Your Majesty,

354
00:16:35,202 --> 00:16:36,961
Xiyan Town is the capital of Xiyan.

355
00:16:37,481 --> 00:16:38,562
But your decrees are sent

356
00:16:38,841 --> 00:16:40,682
from Chenrong Mountain
after your enthronement.

357
00:16:41,122 --> 00:16:42,882
It's inappropriate to go on like this.

358
00:16:43,002 --> 00:16:46,442
Your Majesty,
please relocate the capital to Zhiyi.

359
00:16:49,521 --> 00:16:50,122
Your Majesty.

360
00:16:50,242 --> 00:16:51,122
Please don't.

361
00:16:51,242 --> 00:16:52,562
Xiyan Town has been the capital

362
00:16:52,721 --> 00:16:54,081
since the founding of Xiyan.

363
00:16:54,161 --> 00:16:55,682
How can we just move the capital?

364
00:16:55,762 --> 00:16:56,882
Xiyan boasts

365
00:16:57,562 --> 00:16:58,641
a vast territory,

366
00:16:58,682 --> 00:16:59,721
abundant supplies,

367
00:16:59,762 --> 00:17:00,961
and countless talents.

368
00:17:01,481 --> 00:17:02,362
Yet Xiyan Town

369
00:17:02,521 --> 00:17:03,601
is located in the northwest,

370
00:17:03,841 --> 00:17:05,041
surrounded by mountains.

371
00:17:05,121 --> 00:17:06,442
With poor transportation

372
00:17:06,602 --> 00:17:08,041
of supplies and talent,

373
00:17:08,202 --> 00:17:09,121
it can't function

374
00:17:09,202 --> 00:17:10,202
as the capital city.

375
00:17:10,322 --> 00:17:11,722
Xiyan Town is the foundation

376
00:17:11,722 --> 00:17:12,641
of our entire nation.

377
00:17:13,121 --> 00:17:13,922
Moving to Zhiyi

378
00:17:14,161 --> 00:17:15,842
is disrespectful to our ancestors.

379
00:17:15,881 --> 00:17:16,881
Zhiyi is situated

380
00:17:17,121 --> 00:17:18,562
in the heartland of Dahuang

381
00:17:18,562 --> 00:17:19,722
with access to all directions.

382
00:17:20,121 --> 00:17:21,641
Relocating the capital to Zhiyi

383
00:17:21,922 --> 00:17:24,161
will give us access
to supplies and talents.

384
00:17:24,361 --> 00:17:26,442
It will be a policy
that boosts prosperity

385
00:17:26,722 --> 00:17:28,682
and ensures long-term governance.

386
00:17:28,682 --> 00:17:31,041
The Central Plains
are not our native land, after all.

387
00:17:31,082 --> 00:17:33,361
The Central Plains
are within our territory.

388
00:17:33,881 --> 00:17:36,322
How can you say
they are not our native land?

389
00:17:36,922 --> 00:17:37,922
Say no more.

390
00:17:38,962 --> 00:17:39,962
Relocating the capital

391
00:17:40,682 --> 00:17:41,682
is of great importance

392
00:17:42,602 --> 00:17:44,322
and requires proper discussion.

393
00:17:52,521 --> 00:17:53,136
Your Majesty.

394
00:17:55,521 --> 00:17:57,041
Lady Shen invites you over

395
00:17:57,322 --> 00:17:59,202
to have lunch with her.

396
00:18:00,041 --> 00:18:01,041
Miss Chenrong is here,

397
00:18:01,361 --> 00:18:02,722
visiting Lady Shen.

398
00:18:05,161 --> 00:18:06,482
I have some court affairs

399
00:18:06,482 --> 00:18:07,442
to discuss with Grandfather.

400
00:18:07,881 --> 00:18:09,361
I won't go to Lady Shen today.

401
00:18:21,552 --> 00:18:23,856
(Shen Shuhui)

402
00:18:50,281 --> 00:18:51,361
Nice tea.

403
00:18:52,802 --> 00:18:54,082
It's a tribute

404
00:18:54,361 --> 00:18:55,682
from the Beijiang Clan,

405
00:18:56,322 --> 00:18:58,761
allegedly exclusive
to the Xiyan royal family.

406
00:18:59,361 --> 00:19:00,482
It's my first time having it.

407
00:19:01,121 --> 00:19:02,361
If you like it,

408
00:19:02,562 --> 00:19:04,442
I will have the maid pack some

409
00:19:04,641 --> 00:19:05,521
for you to take home.

410
00:19:05,641 --> 00:19:06,241
No need.

411
00:19:06,761 --> 00:19:08,322
I was just indulging in something new.

412
00:19:08,602 --> 00:19:10,482
I might forget it if I take it home.

413
00:19:11,482 --> 00:19:12,202
Naughty girl.

414
00:19:15,962 --> 00:19:16,881
Has His Majesty arrived?

415
00:19:18,401 --> 00:19:19,761
His Majesty went to the Great Emperor.

416
00:19:20,121 --> 00:19:21,121
He won't come over today.

417
00:19:28,682 --> 00:19:29,322
Have some tea.

418
00:19:50,602 --> 00:19:51,401
Grandpa.

419
00:19:51,401 --> 00:19:52,761
Give me one more chance.

420
00:19:54,881 --> 00:19:55,842
No, no.

421
00:19:56,682 --> 00:19:58,442
I've given you three chances.

422
00:19:58,881 --> 00:19:59,641
One last time.

423
00:19:59,922 --> 00:20:01,041
I promise it's the last time.

424
00:20:01,962 --> 00:20:03,041
Deal.

425
00:20:04,176 --> 00:20:06,739
(Great Emperor of Xiyan)

426
00:20:08,761 --> 00:20:10,241
No regrets once you've made a move.

427
00:20:10,761 --> 00:20:11,922
No, no, I haven't moved.

428
00:20:15,521 --> 00:20:16,521
Have you decided?

429
00:20:20,401 --> 00:20:21,802
Why don't you enter, Your Majesty?

430
00:20:24,722 --> 00:20:26,842
This is why I'm guarding the world.

431
00:20:28,361 --> 00:20:29,722
Only by seeing that

432
00:20:30,562 --> 00:20:32,842
can I continue forward with conviction.

433
00:20:35,521 --> 00:20:37,121
Why don't you just walk in?

434
00:20:37,562 --> 00:20:39,962
You sound like
you're jumping into a pit of fire.

435
00:20:47,962 --> 00:20:48,562
Xuan.

436
00:20:49,121 --> 00:20:49,922
Good to see you, Nian.

437
00:20:53,401 --> 00:20:54,722
I haven't settled scores with you.

438
00:20:54,922 --> 00:20:55,922
Both you and her

439
00:20:57,001 --> 00:20:58,041
underestimated me

440
00:20:58,041 --> 00:20:58,842
and drove me away.

441
00:20:59,082 --> 00:21:00,202
Am I that unreliable?

442
00:21:00,482 --> 00:21:01,121
Of course not.

443
00:21:01,962 --> 00:21:03,001
You're the most reliable.

444
00:21:04,161 --> 00:21:05,161
Except when you cheat.

445
00:21:07,001 --> 00:21:07,761
Grandpa.

446
00:21:07,881 --> 00:21:09,241
Xuan is bullying me.

447
00:21:11,401 --> 00:21:12,682
Will you help me or him?

448
00:21:13,521 --> 00:21:14,962
I'll help whoever calls me sister.

449
00:21:15,722 --> 00:21:16,521
Sister.

450
00:21:17,202 --> 00:21:18,521
Sister.

451
00:21:18,842 --> 00:21:20,442
Sister...

452
00:21:20,962 --> 00:21:21,761
Alright.

453
00:21:22,121 --> 00:21:23,281
I'll help you, alright?

454
00:21:24,121 --> 00:21:25,641
Why did you come at this hour?

455
00:21:26,322 --> 00:21:27,322
Did something come up?

456
00:21:30,482 --> 00:21:31,024
Yes.

457
00:21:31,602 --> 00:21:32,208
Grandfather.

458
00:21:42,041 --> 00:21:42,922
I am planning

459
00:21:46,041 --> 00:21:48,322
to take someone from
the Shangyang Clan as my consort.

460
00:22:05,641 --> 00:22:06,224
Xiaoyao.

461
00:22:07,281 --> 00:22:07,824
I...

462
00:22:12,482 --> 00:22:13,641
I don't mean to take a consort.

463
00:22:14,562 --> 00:22:15,962
I want to avoid warfare.

464
00:22:16,922 --> 00:22:17,802
Of course, I know.

465
00:22:18,802 --> 00:22:20,281
Grandfather passed the throne to you.

466
00:22:20,641 --> 00:22:22,281
Naturally, you can't let him down.

467
00:22:22,881 --> 00:22:24,562
To convince the old clans of Xiyan

468
00:22:24,562 --> 00:22:25,602
to relocate the capital

469
00:22:25,962 --> 00:22:27,041
and give up on the Fifth King,

470
00:22:27,802 --> 00:22:29,802
bonding and reasoning
with them is not enough.

471
00:22:30,761 --> 00:22:32,361
You have to benefit them.

472
00:22:38,682 --> 00:22:39,922
Don't congratulate me.

473
00:22:41,442 --> 00:22:42,161
Understand?

474
00:22:45,082 --> 00:22:45,722
I know.

475
00:22:48,802 --> 00:22:49,401
Go back.

476
00:22:52,922 --> 00:22:53,521
Xuan.

477
00:22:56,202 --> 00:22:56,962
I feel that

478
00:22:56,962 --> 00:22:58,082
you're a bit upset.

479
00:22:58,722 --> 00:23:00,761
Should I accompany you for a walk?

480
00:23:02,442 --> 00:23:04,082
I have a pile of work to do.

481
00:23:05,121 --> 00:23:06,482
How can I afford to be upset?

482
00:23:07,401 --> 00:23:08,682
Be at ease and go back.

483
00:23:11,001 --> 00:23:11,568
Okay.

484
00:23:12,962 --> 00:23:13,761
Then I'll go back.

485
00:23:14,041 --> 00:23:14,842
Okay.

486
00:23:14,842 --> 00:23:18,928
♪You appear at the end of the river♪

487
00:23:19,274 --> 00:23:23,018
♪But disappear as clouds rise♪

488
00:23:23,626 --> 00:23:27,594
♪You appear when I look up♪

489
00:23:27,946 --> 00:23:31,722
♪But disappear as I lower my head♪

490
00:23:32,336 --> 00:23:36,298
♪You appear in the snow♪

491
00:23:36,528 --> 00:23:40,629
♪But disappear as flowers bloom♪

492
00:23:40,976 --> 00:23:43,178
♪You appear as the smoke rises♪

493
00:23:43,178 --> 00:23:48,752
♪You disappear in the light♪

494
00:23:49,584 --> 00:23:52,464
♪You disappear♪

495
00:23:54,288 --> 00:23:57,258
♪In the light♪

496
00:24:05,562 --> 00:24:06,241
What are you doing?

497
00:24:07,401 --> 00:24:09,041
I'm going to find Cang Xuan.

498
00:24:09,761 --> 00:24:10,521
Nian.

499
00:24:12,521 --> 00:24:15,322
Why do you want to find him?

500
00:24:19,121 --> 00:24:19,682
Grandpa.

501
00:24:22,121 --> 00:24:23,361
I like Xuan.

502
00:24:23,842 --> 00:24:24,922
I want to marry him.

503
00:24:25,922 --> 00:24:26,442
Grandpa.

504
00:24:26,722 --> 00:24:28,682
Will you make him marry me, please?

505
00:24:28,802 --> 00:24:29,322
Nian.

506
00:24:29,521 --> 00:24:30,602
You're free to drink.

507
00:24:30,761 --> 00:24:31,881
But don't act crazy.

508
00:24:32,322 --> 00:24:33,001
Nian.

509
00:24:34,361 --> 00:24:35,922
I really like him.

510
00:24:36,482 --> 00:24:37,121
Grandpa.

511
00:24:37,682 --> 00:24:39,322
Grandpa, can you help me, please?

512
00:24:40,482 --> 00:24:41,072
Fine.

513
00:24:41,881 --> 00:24:43,761
I will help you.

514
00:24:46,761 --> 00:24:47,281
Really?

515
00:24:48,442 --> 00:24:49,482
Grandpa, you've agreed?

516
00:24:51,161 --> 00:24:52,482
I never go back on my word.

517
00:24:54,602 --> 00:24:55,722
Would you stop it?

518
00:24:57,202 --> 00:24:58,281
That's enough.

519
00:25:00,722 --> 00:25:01,241
Nian.

520
00:25:03,922 --> 00:25:04,922
That's great.

521
00:25:07,962 --> 00:25:09,361
Grandpa finally said yes.

522
00:25:10,202 --> 00:25:11,001
Finally...

523
00:25:15,322 --> 00:25:17,082
I can marry Cang Xuan.

524
00:25:23,202 --> 00:25:23,922
Grandfather.

525
00:25:24,361 --> 00:25:25,722
How can you lie to her?

526
00:25:26,041 --> 00:25:26,922
She will believe it.

527
00:25:28,241 --> 00:25:30,442
Nian is a sweet little girl,

528
00:25:31,121 --> 00:25:33,082
innocent, unruly, pure, and clever.

529
00:25:33,641 --> 00:25:34,842
She doesn't have

530
00:25:35,121 --> 00:25:36,802
those complicated schemes.

531
00:25:37,482 --> 00:25:38,128
You should

532
00:25:38,322 --> 00:25:39,442
really learn from her.

533
00:25:40,281 --> 00:25:41,082
Be more willful

534
00:25:41,482 --> 00:25:42,401
and more unrestrained.

535
00:25:44,121 --> 00:25:45,722
I can't be willful or unrestrained

536
00:25:45,722 --> 00:25:47,281
because of you and Cang Xuan.

537
00:25:50,442 --> 00:25:52,881
What do you mean by that?

538
00:25:53,401 --> 00:25:54,241
If I say I want to

539
00:25:54,761 --> 00:25:56,241
hang out with Xiang Liu,

540
00:25:56,562 --> 00:25:57,401
would you agree?

541
00:26:02,562 --> 00:26:03,202
No.

542
00:26:05,041 --> 00:26:07,562
Cang Xuan is bound to have
a decisive battle with him.

543
00:26:07,962 --> 00:26:09,442
You hold different stances.

544
00:26:10,001 --> 00:26:10,640
You see,

545
00:26:11,121 --> 00:26:12,521
my bloodline makes it impossible

546
00:26:12,682 --> 00:26:13,881
for me to do as I please.

547
00:26:14,401 --> 00:26:14,960
So,

548
00:26:15,281 --> 00:26:16,761
why should I lie to myself?

549
00:26:20,241 --> 00:26:20,784
Nian.

550
00:26:33,041 --> 00:26:34,602
Why is Your Majesty in a bad mood?

551
00:26:37,682 --> 00:26:39,161
I once thought

552
00:26:39,881 --> 00:26:41,202
the moment I turned Zijin Peak

553
00:26:41,401 --> 00:26:42,641
into Zhaoyun Peak,

554
00:26:43,281 --> 00:26:44,641
I could return to the past.

555
00:26:47,322 --> 00:26:48,722
But even if I plant phoenix trees

556
00:26:48,722 --> 00:26:50,001
all over Chenrong Mountain,

557
00:26:50,001 --> 00:26:51,082
what then?

558
00:26:53,482 --> 00:26:54,322
One wrong step

559
00:26:54,842 --> 00:26:55,842
leads to a wrong path.

560
00:26:57,562 --> 00:26:59,401
I don't think I have any chances now.

561
00:27:00,881 --> 00:27:02,121
Which step was wrong?

562
00:27:03,482 --> 00:27:04,922
I have no idea, either.

563
00:27:07,962 --> 00:27:08,962
All along the way,

564
00:27:09,922 --> 00:27:11,361
it seemed like every step

565
00:27:11,401 --> 00:27:12,241
was the only choice.

566
00:27:13,722 --> 00:27:14,962
But it just turned out

567
00:27:19,121 --> 00:27:19,881
to be wrong.

568
00:27:23,281 --> 00:27:25,281
Even if there are mistakes,

569
00:27:25,802 --> 00:27:26,641
it doesn't matter.

570
00:27:27,401 --> 00:27:28,881
Withered trees can thrive again.

571
00:27:29,041 --> 00:27:29,881
Let alone people.

572
00:27:30,202 --> 00:27:31,041
Where there's a will,

573
00:27:31,202 --> 00:27:32,241
there's a way, for sure.

574
00:27:35,041 --> 00:27:36,161
Is there really a way?

575
00:27:36,641 --> 00:27:37,401
Of course.

576
00:27:37,641 --> 00:27:38,881
There is nothing you can't do,

577
00:27:39,001 --> 00:27:39,842
Your Majesty.

578
