Only you can persuade him.

588
00:28:18,361 --> 00:28:18,962
Father.

589
00:28:20,881 --> 00:28:21,488
Father.

590
00:28:31,602 --> 00:28:33,041
I don't have the power

591
00:28:33,802 --> 00:28:36,401
to rule the court anymore.

592
00:28:37,322 --> 00:28:37,968
Great Emperor.

593
00:28:38,361 --> 00:28:39,281
It's time for medicine.

594
00:28:54,722 --> 00:28:56,281
You two may leave.

595
00:29:04,682 --> 00:29:06,001
Please take care of yourself.

596
00:29:07,682 --> 00:29:08,442
I take my leave.

597
00:29:08,842 --> 00:29:09,641
I take my leave.

598
00:29:23,881 --> 00:29:25,322
Why did you stop me just now?

599
00:29:26,482 --> 00:29:27,442
Cang Xuan has been

600
00:29:27,442 --> 00:29:28,962
establishing his power in court.

601
00:29:29,281 --> 00:29:30,802
If Father doesn't stop him,

602
00:29:31,281 --> 00:29:32,016
then he will

603
00:29:32,082 --> 00:29:33,161
surely relocate the capital

604
00:29:33,161 --> 00:29:34,082
despite our opposition.

605
00:29:43,562 --> 00:29:45,082
Father no longer has the power.

606
00:29:46,521 --> 00:29:48,641
We are unable to stop Cang Xuan now.

607
00:29:50,562 --> 00:29:51,322
However,

608
00:29:52,881 --> 00:29:54,241
it may not be bad

609
00:29:54,722 --> 00:29:56,761
if he insists on relocating the capital.

610
00:29:57,602 --> 00:29:58,521
Why is that?

611
00:30:02,922 --> 00:30:04,442
Such an act

612
00:30:04,602 --> 00:30:06,202
will surely offend the majority

613
00:30:06,202 --> 00:30:08,401
of the old clans who are against it.

614
00:30:09,802 --> 00:30:11,361
The more opposition he gets,

615
00:30:14,322 --> 00:30:15,521
the better for us.

616
00:30:17,241 --> 00:30:17,962
That's right.

617
00:30:19,881 --> 00:30:21,641
They won't change the capital city.

618
00:30:21,962 --> 00:30:22,482
Then,

619
00:30:23,241 --> 00:30:24,602
it's time to change the king.

620
00:30:43,322 --> 00:30:43,842
Grandfather,

621
00:30:44,281 --> 00:30:46,521
what do you think
about relocating the capital?

622
00:30:54,082 --> 00:30:56,482
What I think doesn't matter.

623
00:30:57,442 --> 00:30:59,641
What matters is what Cang Xuan will do.

624
00:31:00,001 --> 00:31:01,922
Relocating capital has always met with

625
00:31:02,082 --> 00:31:03,562
great resistance in history.

626
00:31:03,842 --> 00:31:05,281
If not handled carefully,

627
00:31:06,041 --> 00:31:08,322
the ministers may turn against the king

628
00:31:08,322 --> 00:31:09,641
and stir up trouble.

629
00:31:10,281 --> 00:31:11,361
It may even lead to

630
00:31:11,761 --> 00:31:13,722
something like
the Five Princes Rebellion

631
00:31:14,281 --> 00:31:16,361
back in Haoling.

632
00:31:21,722 --> 00:31:23,761
(The Shangyang lady
has recorded merits.)

633
00:31:24,082 --> 00:31:25,442
(Attired in fine garments,)

634
00:31:25,562 --> 00:31:26,761
(she is gentle and compliant,)

635
00:31:26,922 --> 00:31:28,281
(wise and intelligent.)

636
00:31:28,482 --> 00:31:30,001
(Possessing a graceful presence,)

637
00:31:30,161 --> 00:31:31,562
(she is known for her kind nature.)

638
00:31:31,761 --> 00:31:33,602
(She is hereby titled a consort.)

639
00:31:34,041 --> 00:31:36,322
(I hope she remains
sincere, filial, humble,)

640
00:31:36,442 --> 00:31:37,962
(respectful and frugal.)

641
00:31:38,482 --> 00:31:40,922
(The head of the Shangyang Clan
has been loyal and upright.)

642
00:31:41,202 --> 00:31:42,442
(He has been grateful,)

643
00:31:42,842 --> 00:31:44,161
(dignified, and righteous)

644
00:31:44,361 --> 00:31:45,482
(while safeguarding the nation.)

645
00:31:45,842 --> 00:31:47,241
(Such a man deserves appreciation.)

646
00:31:47,482 --> 00:31:49,001
(I hereby bestow him with)

647
00:31:49,281 --> 00:31:51,161
(the Qingyao Mountain as a reward.)

648
00:31:56,082 --> 00:31:57,641
"Possessing a graceful presence,

649
00:31:58,041 --> 00:31:59,401
she is known for her kind nature."

650
00:32:05,442 --> 00:32:06,281
Miss.

651
00:32:06,602 --> 00:32:07,802
The phrases in the decree

652
00:32:07,802 --> 00:32:09,562
are always exaggerated and polished.

653
00:32:09,722 --> 00:32:11,361
Please don't take it too seriously.

654
00:32:17,881 --> 00:32:18,521
Miss.

655
00:32:19,041 --> 00:32:20,682
Why don't you play the zither?

656
00:32:22,962 --> 00:32:24,602
No one is here to listen to it.

657
00:32:25,202 --> 00:32:26,521
What's the point of playing it?

658
00:32:27,761 --> 00:32:30,281
Back then, we played
the zither and flute together

659
00:32:31,001 --> 00:32:31,962
throughout the night.

660
00:32:33,001 --> 00:32:33,802
But now,

661
00:32:34,482 --> 00:32:35,962
it's hard to just meet each other.

662
00:32:36,722 --> 00:32:37,322
Maybe

663
00:32:37,322 --> 00:32:38,722
we can ask the young master to help.

664
00:32:39,121 --> 00:32:40,121
Times have changed.

665
00:32:41,001 --> 00:32:42,881
My brother can advise on state matters,

666
00:32:43,442 --> 00:32:45,121
but not on His Majesty's
personal affairs.

667
00:32:46,161 --> 00:32:46,802
Then,

668
00:32:48,001 --> 00:32:49,082
let's get Madam here.

669
00:32:54,482 --> 00:32:56,041
My mother may be Madam Chenrong.

670
00:32:56,602 --> 00:32:58,121
But she resides in Chishui

671
00:32:58,562 --> 00:33:00,562
and has no idea what's happening here.

672
00:33:01,001 --> 00:33:02,482
She can't be of much help.

673
00:33:03,082 --> 00:33:04,082
So what can we do?

674
00:33:10,761 --> 00:33:12,161
My brother and my mother can't help.

675
00:33:13,041 --> 00:33:14,001
But I have

676
00:33:14,001 --> 00:33:15,602
a sister-in-law on Chenrong Mountain.

677
00:33:15,690 --> 00:33:19,626
(Chenrong Mansion)

678
00:33:21,761 --> 00:33:23,001
This house of yours

679
00:33:23,001 --> 00:33:24,082
has been repaired just fine.

680
00:33:26,442 --> 00:33:28,041
Your Highness, if you like it,

681
00:33:28,161 --> 00:33:29,161
stay here with Xiaoyao

682
00:33:29,161 --> 00:33:30,082
for some days.

683
00:33:30,482 --> 00:33:31,922
I have no sisters.

684
00:33:31,922 --> 00:33:33,281
I'm so lonely here.

685
00:33:34,361 --> 00:33:35,082
Indeed.

686
00:33:36,161 --> 00:33:37,641
We're not like those men

687
00:33:37,641 --> 00:33:39,001
who at least have jobs to do.

688
00:33:39,482 --> 00:33:40,722
We have too much free time.

689
00:33:40,722 --> 00:33:42,602
It really is boring without company.

690
00:33:47,082 --> 00:33:47,602
Xiaoyao.

691
00:33:47,761 --> 00:33:48,881
I heard from my brother

692
00:33:48,922 --> 00:33:50,881
that His Majesty has been distressed

693
00:33:50,881 --> 00:33:52,602
because of the capital relocation.

694
00:33:52,922 --> 00:33:55,121
It's a pity that I can't help at all.

695
00:33:55,442 --> 00:33:56,121
It's okay.

696
00:33:56,562 --> 00:33:57,922
It's the thought that counts.

697
00:33:58,361 --> 00:33:59,442
Cang Xuan will understand.

698
00:34:00,442 --> 00:34:02,082
What's the point of that?

699
00:34:02,442 --> 00:34:03,722
He keeps everything to himself.

700
00:34:04,082 --> 00:34:05,482
He never appreciates it

701
00:34:05,602 --> 00:34:06,641
even if we want to help.

702
00:34:15,202 --> 00:34:16,401
That's right.

703
00:34:16,442 --> 00:34:17,561
It's all his fault.

704
00:34:17,841 --> 00:34:18,962
I'll give him a scolding.

705
00:34:19,401 --> 00:34:20,816
- It's not his fault!
- It's not his fault!

706
00:34:27,088 --> 00:34:27,641
Forget it.

707
00:34:27,641 --> 00:34:28,482
Let's not talk about it.

708
00:34:28,762 --> 00:34:30,121
The weather is so nice.

709
00:34:30,202 --> 00:34:31,601
Let's go out for a stroll.

710
00:34:31,641 --> 00:34:32,240
Good idea.

711
00:34:32,641 --> 00:34:33,601
I haven't been out

712
00:34:33,601 --> 00:34:34,282
for a long while.

713
00:34:39,081 --> 00:34:39,696
Okay.

714
00:34:47,841 --> 00:34:49,042
Let's check out the fabrics.

715
00:34:49,202 --> 00:34:49,840
Okay.

716
00:35:06,922 --> 00:35:07,482
Thank you.

717
