(Tushan Jing)

718
00:35:12,442 --> 00:35:14,561
The nard is spilled. Let it be.

719
00:35:15,161 --> 00:35:17,081
I'll have them repack some for you.

720
00:35:18,922 --> 00:35:19,561
No need.

721
00:35:20,282 --> 00:35:21,482
Thank you, Chief Tushan.

