Fresh out of the pot.
Braised chicken feet.

724
00:35:41,202 --> 00:35:42,042
Braised duck necks.

725
00:35:42,042 --> 00:35:43,121
Braised duck feet.

726
00:35:43,161 --> 00:35:44,601
Come have a look.

727
00:35:44,962 --> 00:35:46,762
Fresh out of the pot.
Braised chicken feet.

728
00:35:46,762 --> 00:35:48,042
Braised duck necks.

729
00:35:48,042 --> 00:35:48,841
Braised duck feet.

730
00:35:49,202 --> 00:35:51,282
Don't miss out as you pass by!

731
00:35:51,321 --> 00:35:52,922
Come take a look!

732
00:35:53,242 --> 00:35:54,442
Please take a look.

733
00:35:55,081 --> 00:35:57,161
Would you like some
to go with your drink?

734
00:36:00,944 --> 00:36:01,616
Miss.

