00:36:03,682 --> 00:36:04,202
Miss.

736
00:36:06,962 --> 00:36:07,561
No need.

737
00:36:16,962 --> 00:36:17,522
Miss.

738
00:36:17,522 --> 00:36:18,482
What will you bet on?

739
00:36:18,482 --> 00:36:19,561
What will you bet on?

740
00:36:19,561 --> 00:36:20,841
I don't believe it. I'll bet on...

741
00:36:21,482 --> 00:36:22,000
Big.

742
00:36:22,401 --> 00:36:23,442
I follow your bet.

743
00:36:24,641 --> 00:36:25,161
Small.

744
00:36:25,202 --> 00:36:26,722
- Small.
- Small.

745
00:36:30,288 --> 00:36:32,336
(Lirong Chang)

746
00:36:33,881 --> 00:36:36,121
This lady bets quite boldly.

747
00:36:38,442 --> 00:36:39,881
I run a small business.

748
00:36:40,161 --> 00:36:41,161
You must compensate me.

749
00:36:45,522 --> 00:36:46,522
Alright.

750
00:36:46,561 --> 00:36:47,762
Impressive!

751
00:36:47,762 --> 00:36:49,601
You are truly marvelous.

752
00:36:51,601 --> 00:36:52,601
Don't tell me

753
00:36:53,282 --> 00:36:55,722
she's the girl you like.

754
00:37:00,641 --> 00:37:02,522
I must take a closer look.

755
00:37:02,522 --> 00:37:04,482
The woman who can enthrall my buddy

756
00:37:04,482 --> 00:37:06,042
must be extraordinary.

757
00:37:10,202 --> 00:37:11,401
You are truly marvelous.

758
00:37:11,401 --> 00:37:12,722
What's the point of these trifles?

759
00:37:13,321 --> 00:37:13,841
If we play,

760
00:37:14,561 --> 00:37:15,442
let's play big.

761
00:37:18,682 --> 00:37:19,601
Who dares to play with me?

762
00:37:23,282 --> 00:37:23,962
Why don't you

763
00:37:24,401 --> 00:37:25,522
have a round with her?

764
00:37:25,922 --> 00:37:27,482
Carry her home if you win the bet.

765
00:37:34,401 --> 00:37:34,922
Buddy,

766
00:37:35,282 --> 00:37:36,361
if you don't go out now,

767
00:37:36,361 --> 00:37:37,922
you may lose your love to someone else.

768
00:37:46,641 --> 00:37:47,482
Let's bet on

769
00:37:48,682 --> 00:37:49,361
something new.

770
00:37:49,881 --> 00:37:50,522
