I dare you.

771
00:37:51,801 --> 00:37:53,121
- Bet with him!
- Bet with him!

772
00:37:53,121 --> 00:37:55,841
- Bet with him!
- Bet with him!

773
00:37:57,682 --> 00:37:58,361
Why not?

774
00:37:58,801 --> 00:37:59,361
