775
00:38:00,442 --> 00:38:01,081
The loser

776
00:38:01,081 --> 00:38:02,242
must answer a question

777
00:38:03,242 --> 00:38:03,841
without lying.

778
00:38:05,121 --> 00:38:06,482
That's new.

779
00:38:06,522 --> 00:38:07,042
Okay.

780
00:38:07,561 --> 00:38:08,121
Let's bet.

781
00:38:39,361 --> 00:38:40,042
Sorry.

782
00:38:40,121 --> 00:38:40,962
I'm really sorry.

783
00:38:41,561 --> 00:38:42,242
Who

784
00:38:44,121 --> 00:38:45,161
do you like?

785
00:38:48,081 --> 00:38:49,202
What kind of question is that?

786
00:38:52,801 --> 00:38:54,002
What a lousy question.

787
00:38:54,242 --> 00:38:54,841
Next one.

788
00:38:54,962 --> 00:38:56,202
I'll ask whatever I want.

789
00:38:56,841 --> 00:38:58,002
Just answer truthfully.

790
00:38:58,561 --> 00:38:59,641
You lose if you don't answer.

791
00:39:01,722 --> 00:39:02,401
Fine, then.

792
00:39:03,442 --> 00:39:04,561
The person I like...

793
00:39:09,801 --> 00:39:11,401
Is the one I want to spend my life with.

794
00:39:16,962 --> 00:39:18,361
Who do you want to spend your life with?

795
00:39:18,801 --> 00:39:19,682
That's another question.

796
00:39:21,002 --> 00:39:21,922
Let's talk if you win.

797
00:39:32,002 --> 00:39:34,002
She won.

798
00:39:40,442 --> 00:39:41,321
It's my turn.

799
00:39:42,081 --> 00:39:43,601
If you were given another chance,

800
00:39:44,242 --> 00:39:45,801
would you still choose this path?

801
00:39:54,161 --> 00:39:54,672
Yes.

802
00:39:55,922 --> 00:39:56,641
Why?

803
00:40:01,282 --> 00:40:02,561
Because I met someone

804
00:40:05,722 --> 00:40:07,121
very important along the way.

805
00:40:09,561 --> 00:40:11,242
If I had chosen a different path,

806
00:40:13,561 --> 00:40:14,881
I might not have met that person.

807
00:40:21,202 --> 00:40:23,801
You are quite loyal
to your foster father.

808
00:40:30,002 --> 00:40:30,881
This is not fun.

809
00:40:31,321 --> 00:40:32,161
I'm done.

810
00:40:32,841 --> 00:40:33,601
Don't go.

811
00:40:34,841 --> 00:40:35,361
Your money?

812
00:40:35,361 --> 00:40:36,601
Who says she doesn't want the money?

813
00:40:38,962 --> 00:40:40,762
Put all her money into my account.

814
00:40:40,841 --> 00:40:42,242
On what ground?

815
00:40:50,002 --> 00:40:51,561
You're wearing the wrong color

816
00:40:51,561 --> 00:40:52,881
today.

817
00:40:55,682 --> 00:40:56,682
It's not a good omen.

818
00:41:04,482 --> 00:41:05,202
Why were you

819
00:41:05,202 --> 00:41:06,442
gambling alone?

820
00:41:06,561 --> 00:41:08,962
Where is your future husband,
the pride of the day?

821
00:41:15,401 --> 00:41:16,561
You know I'm engaged?

822
00:41:17,722 --> 00:41:20,442
Chief Chishui is engaged
to the Princess of Haoling.

823
00:41:21,121 --> 00:41:22,881
It's hard not to know.

824
00:41:25,121 --> 00:41:26,442
I forgot to congratulate you.

825
00:41:26,801 --> 00:41:27,522
Congratulations.

826
00:41:33,482 --> 00:41:34,442
Don't you have

827
00:41:36,282 --> 00:41:37,081
anything else

828
00:41:37,081 --> 00:41:37,962
to say to me?

829
00:41:45,922 --> 00:41:46,881
What should I say?

830
00:41:58,522 --> 00:41:59,042
Nothing.

831
00:42:00,242 --> 00:42:01,202
There are two things

832
00:42:01,202 --> 00:42:02,321
I'd like to discuss with you.

833
00:42:04,002 --> 00:42:04,528
Go ahead.

834
00:42:05,081 --> 00:42:05,881
The first thing.

835
00:42:07,361 --> 00:42:08,321
I can still make pills

836
00:42:09,161 --> 00:42:10,081
for you right now.

837
00:42:11,242 --> 00:42:12,561
But after I get married,

838
00:42:14,002 --> 00:42:15,522
I won't be able to anymore.

839
00:42:21,002 --> 00:42:21,881
And the second thing?

840
00:42:23,121 --> 00:42:24,561
I want to remove the poisonous bug.

841
00:42:27,682 --> 00:42:29,202
It keeps causing you trouble.

842
00:42:29,762 --> 00:42:30,442
Last time,

843
00:42:31,002 --> 00:42:31,762
you were tired of it.

844
00:42:32,762 --> 00:42:33,922
When you have time,

845
00:42:35,762 --> 00:42:36,482
we'll go to Baili

846
00:42:37,641 --> 00:42:38,841
to remove the poisonous bug.

847
00:42:46,841 --> 00:42:47,482
Rest assured.

848
00:42:48,282 --> 00:42:49,282
After that,

849
00:42:50,202 --> 00:42:51,401
I will still keep my promise

850
00:42:51,401 --> 00:42:52,161
to you.

851
00:42:57,442 --> 00:42:58,042
Alright.

852
00:42:58,601 --> 00:42:59,401
When I have time.

853
00:43:06,321 --> 00:43:07,321
I'll deliver the pills to you

854
00:43:07,321 --> 00:43:08,042
every three months.

855
00:43:08,962 --> 00:43:09,881
I have to go.

856
