857
00:43:41,657 --> 00:43:45,939
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

858
00:43:48,019 --> 00:43:52,819
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

859
00:43:55,955 --> 00:43:58,227
♪Only emptiness remained♪

860
00:44:01,171 --> 00:44:04,243
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

861
00:44:06,092 --> 00:44:10,483
♪I valued all but indifferent
